        "Id": "078d2e51-6560-4121-a47f-b2e81b580ab4",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Much Ado About Muffins",
        "Location": "LOCATION_NORTHAMERICA",
        "PublicId": "122078538598",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/skunk/scene_skunk.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository a07921d5-b47e-4f0a-b8a7-3a5f0d6f0f5a).Image",
        "Description": "Helen West, her son Jed, and her nephew James have all been implicated in the murder of Frank Schmidt. The Schmidts want the death penalty for their slain father, but since the death penalty is abolished in Vermont, they decided to take things into their own hands. That&apos;s where you come in 47.\r\rEliminate the targets and don&apos;t let anyone find you or their corpses. The clients have asked us to do this as cleanly as possible with no collateral damage.\r\rGodspeed 47.",
